<bibRefCitation author="Kovacic, M." box="[552,711,1865,1891]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="1051 - 1055" refId="ref57812" refString="Kovacic, M. (2003) Hyperbenthic gobies in the Kvarner area, Adriatic Sea. Journal of Fish Biology, 63, 1051 - 1055. https: // doi. org / 10.1046 / j. 1095 - 8649.2003.00221. x" type="journal article" year="2003">Kovačić 2003</bibRefCitation>
