<bibRefCitation author="Le Bris, S. &amp; Pillon, R. &amp; Louisy, P." box="[723,937,1865,1892]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" refId="ref59912" refString="Le Bris, S., Pillon, R. &amp; Louisy, P. (2016) Signalisation de / Record of Pseudaphya ferreri, 03 July 2016 (obs. 18 May 2016, photo  2382). Fish Watch Forum, Louisy, P. &amp; Francour, P. (Ed.). Available from: https: // www. fish-watch. org (accessed 28 September 2021)" type="url" year="2016">
